post.title: Fuller House, why'd you watch it?
post.body: I'm just curious if anyone watched Fuller House and why they watched it. Me personally for nostalgia, I never expected a good show because lets be honest, the original Full House was super corny but as a kid it was one of the few shows that aired before my bed time and I guess I fell in love with it. With the remake, now I'm just reminded of how bad and corny it was. Thoughts?
